Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:03.71,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:05.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That should be all of the large boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:08.20,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go say "goodbye" to the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:08.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:13.39,shirt,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Team Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet will \Nbe at the nationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.45,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:27.67,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me become a Class A player!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won't beat me next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:33.67,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.01,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.59,0:00:44.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again when we \Nbecome Class A players!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:50.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:23.97,Chiha-title,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:33.37,Chiha-ep-title-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}A Whirlwind \Nof Flower \NPetals \NDescends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:33.26,Chiha-ep-title-verse,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, this is our stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were you daydreaming or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:57.06,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you been in touch with Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:02:59.94,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:08.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata must be incredibly strong now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.95,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll see him at this \Nyear's Omi Jingu tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:17.58,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want to play against Arata \Nin the national tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:18.83,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.79,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What class are you right now, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.50,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made Class B in the \Ntournament during spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:29.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it'll take you another \Nthree years to make Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just stick with track?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of hanging around in \NClass B for three more years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:42.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as violent \Nas you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came all the way here \Nto show you my uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:51.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.70,ta-kun,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}She calls him Ta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.80,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I win the tournament on \NSunday and make Class A,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you have to help me \Nstart a karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.51,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how hard it \Nis to make Class A in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.72,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, who is she, Ta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:27.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him pay for getting \Nhimself a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell somebody!  Anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was calling Taichi "Ta-kun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.49,phone,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata - Home in Fukui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:45.04,phone2,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata - Home in Fukui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.88,bunkyo,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,200)}Bunkyo City\NOtsuka Karuta Memorial Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.42,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.28,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forget.{Orig: I couldn't stop thinking about what she said.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eye!  Eye!  Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.20,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada, I can't believe \Nyou actually recognized me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.56,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are your armpits and \Npubes all bushy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.85,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But not as bushy as your eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:22.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.24,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be quiet while \Nthey're memorizing the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:32.46,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  You're here to \Ncheer for Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks pretty tense in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:44.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They have to win if they want \Nto advance to the next class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.04,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's especially hard \Non the Class B players.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are many strong players\N who spend years in Class B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:53.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because they can't rack up enough wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's trying as hard as they \Ncan to reach the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.26,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I win the tournament \Nand make Class A,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.16,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you have to help me \Nstart a karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.05,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna take you a \Nwhile to make Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:17.06,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows, I heard that you're in the \Nsame high school as Chihaya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.27,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.98,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a karuta club, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.10,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should come practice \Nwith the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:28.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm thinking about \Njoining the soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:30.15,quiet,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please be quiet\N during matches
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.05,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to turn into \Na two-timing bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or you'll never become a Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.98,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I played karuta in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.79,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a small club, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:54.85,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced and became \Nbetter little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.80,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I always knew, deep down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:04.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that I could spend my\N entire youth on karuta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.23,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,without ever becoming \Nbetter than Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:14.96,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:15.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:22.61,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:30.45,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.60,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So spring ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:36.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.85,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you teach her to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.71,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not under normal circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.60,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I gave her a few tips since \Nshe wanted to win so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:50.44,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If someone challenges her, \Nshe's supposed to complain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.60,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,loud enough that everyone in the room can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:57.53,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The hazy early morning light comes not from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.53,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The point is to overwhelm her opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really so obsessed with winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.03,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When Chihaya-chan entered middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.09,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why track?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.96,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There a reason for choosing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:33.10,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you're supposed to start \Nrunning when you hear the starter pistol fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.83,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.61,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.11,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll also help me get in shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.49,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:49.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Spend your entire youth \Nwithout becoming stronger"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hold that thought for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:00.26,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The night was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.59,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.88,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's made it past the third round!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for raising my \Nvoice during the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An okay sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.53,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the chocolate sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.01,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.73,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows, run down to \Nthe convenience store
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and buy some chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!  Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:40.44,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Temporarily Closed\N Sorry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:42.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.62,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Convenience" my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other shops around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go-Godi—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.96,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Temporarily Closed\N Sorry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.86,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\fad(0,530)}Temporarily Closed\NSorry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.23,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Savor them, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.69,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat three of them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.50,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These are good, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.13,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So many different flavors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta tournaments are \Nlong and grueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have to memorize the \Npositions of fifty cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.60,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize, then forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.22,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The longest tournaments require \Nyou to play seven matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.27,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from morning till night,\N before there can be a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.11,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain will burn through \Nthe sugar in your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and you can lose up to three kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So players eat chocolate \Nto recharge themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chihaya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:54.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you've gotten a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.08,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's already asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:05.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's scary is that Chihaya-chan \Nsleeps with her eyes open,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.80,Open,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Open {tly is totally guessing here...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what I like about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.69,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm just making sure that nobody \Nhas to see your ugly mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:38.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.56,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about forcing you into \Nmaking a karuta club with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:45.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win, so watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows, we're allowed to \Nwatch the final match inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass. \N I can't do anything if I'm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll join you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:08.79,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already sick of looking at \Nher opponent, Yasuda-kun's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, he will be a formidable foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:15.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has the ability, but he's been \Nstuck in Class B for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.98,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's fired up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I dare say that his card \Npositioning is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuda-san's gonna win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:26.22,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him losing to some \Nrandom high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at the way he's \Nspreading out the cards
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that start with the same syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.59,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many cards will he beat her by?
