Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.81,shirt2,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}Team Chihayafuru
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.84,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please be there for me.
