Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:59.20,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.25,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.33,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
