Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as he heard "Im," \Nhe went for the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Impassionate gods" card \Non the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once he heard it was "Impassioned vows",
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.85,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he switched to the correct \Ncard on his own side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuda-kun is known for \Nhis precise aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:55.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting pressure on Chihaya-chan, \Nsince she usually starts slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.22,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.40,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know you well, Ayase Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.23,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Impassionate" is your best card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.26,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once I've taken away \Nyour favorite card,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.74,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it will be easy to break \Nyour 15-year-old spirit.
