Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.67,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It makes perfect sense, Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I teach aggressive karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.90,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The objective is to take cards \Nfrom the opponent's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:56.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it risky to give \Na strong opponent her best card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:15:00.16,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one card Chihaya-chan \Nwill always win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.93,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win, \Nso watch over me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.37,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.87,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata!
