Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They keep passing around \Nthe "Chihaya" card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuda-kun is being really stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:58.46,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he doesn't want to let \NChihaya-chan have an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.83,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of the lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such intensity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:06.35,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is holding her \Nown against Yasuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.83,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While autumn leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.15,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that my...
