Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.06,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:30.95,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.20,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play karuta, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can improve together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:44.30,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we have each other, \Nwe can become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  Stay right here, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:58.56,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:06.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for me to \Ncall Arata now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.74,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.32,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell him that I made Class A.
