Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.24,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.47,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi's also here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.50,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made Class A today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I worked so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.41,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi and I are at \Nthe same high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.30,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He got himself a girlfriend \Nwho calls him Ta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.59,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.38,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dr. Harada's doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.25,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to tell you, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.88,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How strong are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but don't call me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.03,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped playing karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
