Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.27,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.00,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River
